label.value: dorsal flange of the second valvifer

value.value: The flange that extends on the dorsal margin of the second valvifer. Part of the ventral T9-second valvifer muscle attaches to the flange.
The pronoto-procoxal muscle that arises dorsomedially from the pronotum.

label.value: dorsal ramus of the first valvula

value.value: The region that extends along the dorsal margin of the first valvula and bears the aulax.
